          "ID": "Start",
          "Text": "Oh! Hello there. I'm Cinnamon Bun. Things have gone a bit sideways at the bakery — a soot gremlin got in, and in the fuss it knocked my late wife's keepsake somewhere out east. Could you help an old bun out?",
          "Choices": [
            {
